<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 23 May 2026 12:52:50 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a11a31f04498</link><description>&lt;p&gt;意大利米兰大教堂内部&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Church interior, view on the two organs inside the Duomo of Milan. In the bottom right there is a richly ornamented dome shaped structure with a statue of a bishop next to it - most likely a grave. In the front we see church benches." height="4661" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/buzz/6a11a31f04498.jpg" width="3107"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://buzz.some.pics"&gt;@buzz&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2026 12:52:50 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a119c84ec066</link><description>&lt;p&gt;会议后。荷兰莱顿的彼得教堂。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Light falls in beams through a gothic church window on empty tables with high barstools. The pillars in the church rise up to an arched ceiling. There are no people in the picture." height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/buzz/6a119c84ec066.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://buzz.some.pics"&gt;@buzz&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2026 12:24:40 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>乌菲兹美术馆</title><link>https://some.pics/6a11944ae5864</link><description>&lt;p&gt;乌菲兹美术馆，佛罗伦萨&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Two story building with high arched windows on the first floor. The bottom floor has an arched opening giving a view of another part of the Uffizi. In front of the building are people admiring the architecture." height="1828" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/buzz/6a11944ae5864.jpg" width="1219"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://buzz.some.pics"&gt;@buzz&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2026 11:49:33 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a118e60a321e</link><description>&lt;p&gt;心在奇怪的地方&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Grey and white silos in an industrial area where a rather small red heart is painted on one,  and a white heart on another. " height="1802" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a118e60a321e.jpg" width="2202"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2026 11:24:19 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>小憩</title><link>https://some.pics/6a1188065116c</link><description>&lt;p&gt;片刻的休息。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Two wooden rakes in sunny grass." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a1188065116c.jpg" width="1125"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 23 May 2026 10:57:13 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>